ðŸ§± Tech Stack Breakdown
Layer	Tech/Service	Purpose
Frontend	HTML/CSS/JS (or React)	Web UI
Backend API	C# (.NET Core Web API) OR Node.js	Game logic, matchmaking
Containers	Docker	Package frontend/backend
Cluster	Amazon EKS	Orchestration
Ingress	AWS ALB Ingress Controller	Load balancing traffic
CI/CD	GitHub Actions / CodePipeline	Auto deploy containers
DevOps Tool	Cloud9 / local dev	Coding & config
Database	Amazon RDS (PostgreSQL) or DynamoDB	Game state, users
Static Assets	Amazon S3 + CloudFront (optional)	Frontend hosting
